ul justification of each object\u00e2\u0080\u0099s contribution beyond mere description", "Logical structure, correctly labeled captions, and traceable citations supporting academic integrity"], "weaknesses": ["Occasional over-generalizations about human evolution and capitalism that reduce precision", "Some conflation between human and machine bias mechanisms", "Inconsistent referencing format affecting scholarly polish"], "calculationMethod": "Holistic AI evaluation: The exhibition meets all core requirements at a very high level, clearly situating three specific artefacts in context and explicitly linking them to IA prompt 12 with nuanced discussions of affinity, Barnum and algorithmic confirmation biases. Strong quantitative evidence (e.g. 47% injury differential, COMPAS error rates) and historical data (e.g. 99% male engineers) underpin sophisticated analyses of perspective, justification and inevitability. The structure is logical and academic integrity is upheld through captions and citations. Minor imprecision arises from occasional over-generalizations and inconsistent referencing, but these do not substantially detract from the coherent, evidence-based demonstration of how TOK manifests in the world. A score of 9 accurately reflects this very high but not entirely flawless performance.", "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}], "strandSelections": [{"versionId": "59279870-1587-427d-a2a1-21c37bd53aa8", "strandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "selectedBandId": "5552e9fd-0d0a-4bb2-9ece-5e7a3c438771", "bandScore": 9, "reasoning": "$49"}], "annotations": [{"id": "da8121e9-08a3-4d6e-8337-0bde92b1c190", "versionId": "59279870-1587-427d-a2a1-21c37bd53aa8", "criterionId": null, "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.0888, "y": 0.6848, "width": 0.41500000000000004, "height": 0.18700000000000006}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0888, "y": 0.6848}, {"x": 0.5038, "y": 0.6848}, {"x": 0.5038, "y": 0.8718}, {"x": 0.0888, "y": 0.8718}], "comment": 